      <p>Please refer to the <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en-US">Google Privacy Policy</a> for more information on how Google handles your data and how you can control your privacy settings for Google Ads.</p>

      <h3>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h3>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page.</p>

      <h3>Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:akatsuki2555@waifu.club">akatsuki2555@waifu.club</a>.</p>
